MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 517

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF LA FORTUNA NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL, CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED AT BARANGAY LA FORTUNA, MUNICIPALITY OF SOCORRO, PROVINCE OF ORIENTAL MINDORO, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from entry, sale, disposition or settlement, and thereby reserve for school site purposes of La Fortuna National High School under the Administration of the Department of Education, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated at Barangay La Fortuna, Municipality of Socorro, Province of Oriental Mindoro, which parcels of land are more particularly described as follows:

TECHNICAL DESCRIPTIONS

LOT NO. 1452-A, Csd-04-021376-D

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 1452-A, Csd-04-021376-D, identical to Lot No. 13502, Cad-647-D, a portion of Lot No. 1452, Cad-647-D, Socorro Cadastre) situated in Barangay La Fortuna, Municipality of Socorro, Province of Oriental Mindoro, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the NW., along lines 1-2-3 by Lot 1434, Cad-647-D, Socorro Cadastre, on the NE., along lines 3-4-5-6-7-8-9 by Lot 1433, Cad-647-D, Socorro Cadastre, on the SE., along lines 9-10-11-12 by Lot 1452-C, Csd-04-021376-D, identical to Lot 13504, Cad-647-D, a portion of Lot 1452, Cad-647-D, Socorro Cadastre, and on SW., along line 12-1 by Lot 1431, Cad-647-D, Socorro Cadastre.

